label: A2B3_cP60_212_acd_bce-001
title: $\gamma$-Fe$_{2}$O$_{3}$ ($D5_{7}$) Structure
comments:
(Hermann, 1937) gives $\gamma$-Al$_{2}$O$_{3}$ as the prototype for {\em Strukturbericht} $D5_{7}$, but states that the data for $\gamma$-Fe$_{2}$O$_{3}$ is more reliable and presents the data for the later compound, which we use as the prototype. 
 More information about the Al$_{2}$O$_{3}$ compounds can be found on the \href{current_web_home_dir/A2B3_hR10_167_c_e-001}{corundum ($D5_{1}$) page}. 
 This is a \href{current_web_home_dir/AB_cF8_225_a_b-001}{rock-salt ($B1$) structure with defects}.  
 This structure can also be expressed in the enantiomorphic space group $P4_{1}32$ \#213.
